verbose_text: Quantitative analysis of the maximum plaque diameters of each group revealed that the maximum plaque diameters of non induced not melanin producing GLV-1h462 infected A549 cells were significantly (p < 0.001) bigger (maximum diameter : 124 +/- 32mum) than those of induced melanin synthesizing GLV-1h462 infected cells (71 +/- 31mum) or GLV-1h460 infected A549 in the absence (67 +/- 24mum) or presence (62 +/- 22mum) of dox.
evidence: melanin synthesizing GLV-1h462 infected cells (71 +/- 31mum) or GLV-1h460
